{"tid":220632,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾意養貓就好似鍾意溝靚女咁","createTime":"2017-04-28T06:01:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-30T11:25:56.000Z","uid":31058,"like":35,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"78de141ca180bcbac440383cd2a2c9ae1536a50d","tid":220632,"uid":31058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T06:01:52.000Z","msg":"都係人嘅本性。<br />\n<br />\n高登一向都多人鍾意貓 包括小弟 但眾所週知養嘅巴絲唔會叫自己隻貓做寵物 而係叫主人<br />\n<br />\n貓性格高傲 而且並無狗對主人個種忠心 你有好處俾到佢咪走埋黎 無嘅話半眼都唔會望下你 更唔好提貓係小數會虐待其他動物作樂嘅生物<br />\n<br />\n但呢d 問題都唔會影響佢地嘅吸引力。<br />\n<br />\n因為貓個死人樣好撚可愛 隻肉球掌好撚得意 就算佢抓爛你張梳發 整亂你間屋 只要扮下可憐樣 你都係會心軟<br />\n<br />\n因為外觀吸引 性格幾差 行為幾惡劣 大家都會接受 <br />\n<br />\n呢個就係人嘅本性。<br />\n<br />\n利申 無養貓 只係有感以發"},{"pid":"7bd12e70f7c2c384478b7d9beaae819eaef052b7","tid":220632,"uid":58914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T06:16:18.000Z","msg":"駁唔到"},{"pid":"77f56d0a68334669a302faaf758470b5940c7de6","tid":220632,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T06:24:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"392bdf65d8946969547cb55a39ed432f6a7895be","tid":220632,"uid":31058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T07:00:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無錯<br />\n人就是咁犯賤</blockquote><br />\n不可抗力"},{"pid":"0acc8a90b9647619366985879acc76481252d31d","tid":220632,"uid":31058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T07:53:59.000Z","msg":"有冇貓主發表下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac6ce61ad9e13a6d59efeced990d37bc8259eae0","tid":220632,"uid":73202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T07:59:16.000Z","msg":"我養狗<br />\n所以好注重性格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2099bb1649f0ea0eda6871ff7084c4e5eee65f19","tid":220632,"uid":31058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:45:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我養狗<br />\n所以好注重性格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class